metatags.og:description: Photos which appear to show a doll named ‘Abortion Barbie’ have been shared widely online in the United States, Africa and elsewhere. While many readers have interpreted the picture as a dark joke or a political statement, others have taken it seriously. In fact, the doll was created by a conservative US street artist as part of a 2014 campaign against a Texas politician who favoured less restrictive abortion laws.
